#NoEnv
SendMode Input
SetCapsLockState, AlwaysOff

CapsLock & Backspace:: Delete

CapsLock & i:: Up
CapsLock & k:: Down
CapsLock & j:: Left
CapsLock & l:: Right

CapsLock & u:: PgUp
CapsLock & o:: PgDn

CapsLock & h:: Home
CapsLock & Ö:: End

CapsLock & p:: Ins

CapsLock & r:: send {Blind}{LCtrl}{r}
CapsLock & x:: send {Blind}{LCtrl}{x}
CapsLock & c:: send {Blind}{LCtrl}{c}
CapsLock & v:: send {Blind}{LCtrl}{v}

CapsLock & (:: send {Blind}{[}
CapsLock & ):: send {Blind}{]}
CapsLock & /:: send {Blind}{{}
CapsLock & =:: send {Blind}{}}
CapsLock & q:: send {Blind}{@}
CapsLock & e:: send {Blind}{€}
CapsLock & ß:: send {Blind}{\}
CapsLock & +:: send {Blind}{~}
CapsLock & <:: send {Blind}{|}
CapsLock & 2:: send {Blind}{²}
CapsLock & 3:: send {Blind}{³}
